# duti settings — applied via: duti ~/.duti
# Format: app_id  UTI/extension  role

# VS Code: default editor for all plain/ASCII text documents
com.microsoft.VSCode    public.plain-text         all
com.microsoft.VSCode    public.utf8-plain-text    all

# VS Code: source code & markup (by UTI where clean, extension otherwise)
